      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="row free-for-oss">
    <section class="landing-centered-wrapper">
      <div class="large-12 columns">
        <h2>Testing your open source<br class="mobile-no-break"/> projects will always be free!</h2>
        <p><em>Seriously. Always.</em> We like to think of it as our way of giving
          <br class="mobile-no-break"/>back to a community that connects so many people.</p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <div class="spacer"></div>

