          <li>
            <img src="../images/svg/stage-passed.svg" alt="" class="checkmark"> Auto deployments on passing builds</li>
          <li>
            <img src="../images/svg/stage-passed.svg" alt="" class="checkmark"> Clean VMs for every build</li>
